
  Poliwrath    Water Type Pokémon

  An adept swimmer at both the 
  front crawl and breast stroke. 
   Easily overtakes the best human 
  swimmers. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Poliwag ► Poliwhirl ► Poliwrath

